20three%20decades%20after%20the%20introduction%20of%20a%20cap%20on%20the%20number%20of%20children%20public%20representatives%20have%20at%20the%20third%20tier%20of%20governance.%20Naidu's%20government%20has%20now%20removed%20this%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Small%20Window%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20reassessed%20the%20law%20after%20realising%20the%20need%20to%20address%20the%20state's%20demographic%20imbalance.%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Total%20Fertility%20Rate%20(TFR)%20is%20around%201.7%2C%20well%20below%20the%202.1%20norm%20that%20is%20typically%20considered%20necessary%20for%20stabilising%20a%20population.%20By%20next%20year%2C%20the%20state's%20population%20is%20expected%20to%20reach%2053.8%20million%2C%20growing%20to%2054.4%20million%20a%20decade%20later.%20However%2C%20projections%20suggest%20that%20by%202041%2C%20the%20population%20will%20begin%20to%20decline%2C%20potentially%20dropping%20to%2054.2%20million.%20These%20statistics%2C%20cited%20by%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20underscore%20the%20reasons%20behind%20his%20new%20call%20for%20policy%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20United%20Nations%20report%20published%20in%20September%202023%20estimated%20that%2010.5%25%20of%20Indians%20are%20currently%20aged%2060%20and%20above.%20This%20proportion%20is%20expected%20to%20rise%20to%2015%25%20in%20a%20decade%2C%20and%20by%202046%2C%20the%20number%20of%20elderly%20people%20will%20surpass%20the%20number%20of%20children%20aged%200-14%2C%20while%20the%20population%20of%20those%20aged%2015-59%20will%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20state%20leader%2C%20especially%20one%20who%20is%20credited%20with%20putting%20undivided%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20on%20a%20rapid%20development%20path%2C%20cannot%20afford%20to%20dismiss%20concerns%20about%20an%20ageing%20population%20and%20the%20challenges%20it%20brings.%20Naidu%20is%20not%20the%20only%20leader%20to%20highlight%20the%20need%20for%20demographic%20correction.%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20M.K.%20Stalin%20has%20also%20suggested%20that%20people%20in%20the%20state%20should%20have%20more%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Logic%20Behind%20The%20Call%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20there%20more%20to%20this%20than%20meets%20the%20eye%3F%20There%20is%20a%20context%20to%20the%20recent%20calls%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20chief%20ministers%20to%20encourage%20people%20to%20have%20larger%20families.%20The%20proposed%20delimitation%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20is%20one%20such%20trigger.%20The%20process%20will%20adjust%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20per%20state%20based%20on%20population%2C%20and%20southern%20states%20fear%20their%20political%20representation%20will%20decline%20compared%20to%20northern%20states%2C%20where%20the%20population%20continues%20to%20grow%20at%20a%20faster%20clip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20simple%20calculation%20based%20on%20population%20growth%20rates%20since%20the%20turn%20of%20the%20century%20shows%20this%20shift.%20In%20southern%20states%2C%20the%20birth%20rate%20has%20fallen%20from%202.6%20to%201.5%2C%20which%20directly%20correlates%20with%20a%20potential%20reduction%20in%20the%20number%20of%20seats.%20In%20contrast%2C%20northern%20states%20have%20maintained%20birth%20rates%20well%20above%20the%202.1%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20logic%20was%20evident%20back%20in%202001%2C%20when%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee's%20government%20froze%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20until%202025%2C%20after%20southern%20parties%20argued%20that%20states%20that%20had%20managed%20population%20growth%20better%20should%20not%20be%20penalised.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20a%20limited%20redrawing%20of%20constituency%20boundaries%20was%20carried%20out%20without%20increasing%20the%20total%20number%20of%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELimits%20To%20Delimitation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwenty-five%20years%20later%2C%20the%20argument%20that%20performing%20states%20should%20not%20be%20penalised%20remains%20valid.%20The%20delimitation%20exercise%2C%20a%20decadal%20process%20until%201971%2C%20was%20then%20frozen%20in%201975%20until%20the%20year%202000.%20In%202001%2C%20it%20was%20delayed%20further%20to%202025.%20However%2C%20this%20process%20must%20wait%20until%20after%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20delayed%20census%2C%20which%20was%20postponed%20five%20years%20ago%20due%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20uncertain%20how%20effective%20Naidu%20and%20Stalin's%20calls%20will%20be%20in%20shifting%20public%20attitudes.%20Encouraging%20people%20to%20abandon%20the%20%E2%80%9CSmall%20is%20Beautiful%E2%80%9D%20slogan%2C%20which%20advocates%20having%20no%20more%20than%20two%20children%2C%20in%20favour%20of%20larger%20families%20will%20not%20be%20an%20easy%20task.%20Studies%20in%20Japan%20and%20elsewhere%20suggest%20that%20changing%20established%20social%20norms%20can%20take%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there%20is%20a%20compelling%20case%20for%20the%20delimitation%20process%20to%20be%20carried%20out%20innovatively.%20Policy%20planners%20and%20lawmakers%20should%20come%20together%20to%20develop%20a%20logical%20and%20pragmatic%20solution%20as%20India%20sets%20its%20sights%20on%20becoming%20a%20developed%20nation%20by%202047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(K.V.%20Prasad%20is%20a%20senior%20Delhi-based%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737631860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fjhdmdru_chandrababu_625x300_23_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fnow-chandrababu-naidu-wants-people-to-have-more-children-7541019%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andhra%20Pradesh's%20TFR%20is%20around%201.7%2C%20well%20below%20the%202.1%20norm%20that%20is%20typically%20considered%20necessary%20for%20stabilising%