score%20of%2096.1.%20The%20top%20ranks%20is%20occupied%20by%20universities%20from%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETHE%20has%20released%20the%20World%20University%20Rankings%20by%20Subject%20for%202025%2C%20covering%2011%20disciplines%3A%20Arts%20and%20Humanities%2C%20Business%20and%20Economics%2C%20Computer%20Science%2C%20Education%20Studies%2C%20Engineering%2C%20Law%2C%20Life%20Sciences%2C%20Medical%20and%20Health%2C%20Physical%20Sciences%2C%20Psychology%2C%20and%20Social%20Sciences.%20The%20US%20dominates%20the%20ranking%20by%20featuring%20in%20nine%20subjects%2C%20while%20UK%20stands%20second%20by%20leading%20in%20the%20other%20two.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%20is%20ranked%20at%20the%20fifth%20position%20with%20an%20overall%20score%20of%2095.8%2C%20University%20of%20Cambridge%20in%20the%20UK%20comes%20at%20the%20sixth%20position%20with%20a%20score%20of%2095.6%2C%20California%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20ranks%20at%20the%20seventh%20position%20with%2095.5%20score%2C%20Princeton%20University%20with%20an%20overall%20score%20of%2094.5%20ranks%20at%20the%20eight%20place%2C%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore%20with%2093.4%20score%20is%20placed%20at%20ninth%20and%20ETH%20Zurich%20with%20a%20score%20of%2092.6%20is%20ranked%20at%20the%20tenth%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Engineering%20subject%2C%20Anna%20University%20follows%20in%20the%20251%E2%80%93300%20range%20with%20scores%20between%2044.7%20and%2046.6.%20Lovely%20Professional%20University%20is%20ranked%20301%E2%80%93400%20with%20a%20score%20range%20of%2041.3%20to%2044.6.%20Both%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia%20and%20Saveetha%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20and%20Technical%20Sciences%20are%20ranked%20401%E2%80%93500%20with%20scores%20ranging%20from%2038.3%20to%2041.2.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737630780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fou2ft9sg_iisc_625x300_10_October_