%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine's%20fighter%20pilots%20are%20using%20Cold%20War%20skills%20the%20West%20deemphasized%20decades%20ago%20but%20may%20need%20again%2C%20former%20US%20pilot%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221801%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20F-16%20fighter%20jets%20flying%20side-by-side%20against%20blue%20skies.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b2c782b4912df3ae197dec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221201%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20F-16s%20are%20seen%20in%20the%20air%20in%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20of%20Ukraine%20on%20August%204.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FValentyn%20Ogirenko%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUkrainian%20pilots%20are%20using%20skills%20that%20Western%20pilots%20have%20let%20atrophy%2C%20a%20former%20F-16%20pilot%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20West%20might%20need%20to%20use%20these%20skills%20again%20in%20a%20great-power%20war%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUkraine's%20fight%20against%20Russia's%20invasion%20is%20giving%20the%20West%20a%20slew%20of%20lessons.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20pilots%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-did-russia-invade-ukraine-putin-politics-motive-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efighting%20against%20Russia's%20invasion%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20using%20flying%20techniques%20the%20West%20has%20not%20really%20used%20since%20the%20Cold%20War%20but%20might%20need%20to%20revive%2C%20a%20former%20US%20F-16%20pilot%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20fight%20has%20offered%20the%20West%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20lessons%20that%20it%20might%20need%20to%20apply%20in%20a%20great-power%20conflict.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERetired%20US%20Air%20Force%20Col.%20John%20Venable%2C%20a%20former%20F-16%20pilot%20and%20defense%20expert%20at%20the%20Mitchell%20Institute%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20one%20of%20those%20lessons%20is%20that%20old%20techniques%20%E2%80%94%20specifically%20low-altitude%20flying%20%E2%80%94%20might%20need%20to%20be%20brought%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Europe%20during%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20flew%20low%20altitude%20all%20of%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Venable%20said%2C%20adding%20they%20%26quot%3Bwere%20practicing%20against%20high-threat%20situations%20where%20you%20have%20surface-to-air%20missiles%20that%20can%20take%20you%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVenable%20retired%20in%202007%20after%20a%2025-year%20career%20in%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%2C%20where%20he%20flew%20the%20F-16%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Europe%2C%20the%20Pacific%2C%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%20He%20had%20more%20than%20more%20than%20300%20hours%20of%20combat%20time%20in%20Kuwait%2C%20Iraq%2C%20and%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20low-altitude%20flying%20to%20evade%20surface-to-air%20threats%20can%20be%20particularly%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20ability%20to%20actually%20fly%20really%20low%20until%20you%20actually%20need%20to%20expose%20yourself%20in%20order%20to%20deliver%20ordinance%20or%20shoot%20another%20aircraft%20down%2C%20that%20skillset%20is%20no%20small%20thing%20to%20grab%20ahold%20of.%20It%20takes%20a%20while%20to%20do%20that.%20And%20in%20the%20process%2C%20you%20lose%20a%20lot%20of%20aircraft%2C%20you%20lose%20a%20lot%20of%20pilots%20because%20of%20collision%20with%20the%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukrainians%20are%20having%20to%20fly%20this%20way%20because%20of%20the%20prolific%20threats%20to%20anything%20in%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20pilots%20%26quot%3Bcome%20in%20really%2C%20really%20low%2C%20and%20then%20they%20pop%20up%26quot%3B%20to%20either%20hit%20an%20air%20or%20ground%20target%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20then%20after%20they're%20done%20dropping%20their%20munitions%20or%20shooting%20their%20missiles%2C%20then%20they%20have%20to%20get%20right%20back%20down%20into%20the%20low-altitude%20environment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3Bthat%20skillset%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Western%20way%20of%20doing%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20%26quot%3Bcontinued%20to%20practice%20low%20altitude%20tactics%20all%20the%20way%20up%20to%20Desert%20Storm%26quot%3B%20in%201991.%20Several%20US%20aircraft%20were%20lost%20in%20the%20early%20days%2C%20so%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20moved%20to%20employ%20medium-altitude%20tactics.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20when%20the%20service%20began%20to%20move%20away%20low-level%20tactics%2C%26quot%3B%20Venable%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20F-16%20fighter%20jets%20fly%20over%20a%20Patriot%20Air%20and%20Missile%20Defense%20System%20aginst%20a%20grey%20sky%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67065c9d198738e3a70f4756%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Ukrainian%20Air%20Force's%20F-16%20fighter%20jets%20fly%20over%20a%20Patriot%20Air%20and%20Missile%20Defense%20System%20in%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20in%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FEfrem%20Lukatsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20hasn't%20had%20to%20fly%20its%20fourth-gen%20fighter%20jets%20into%20contested%20airspace%20in%20decades%2C%20and%20stealth%20platforms%20like%20the%20F-35%20Lightning%20II%20Joint%20Strike%20Fighter%20allow%20pilots%20to%20fly%20at%20higher%20altitudes%20without%20worrying%20as%20much%20about%20surface-to-air%20missiles.%20But%20that%20capability%20could%20be%20eroded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20come%20a%20point%20in%20the%20not-too-distant%20future%20where%20even%20stealth%20platforms%20have%20to%20incorporate%20some%20of%20these%20tactics%20into%20their%20engagements%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20low-altitude%20flying.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20something%20that%20the%20United%20St