20CEO%20Dara%20Khosrowshahi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20told%20a%20small%20gathering%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20a%20Q%26amp%3BA.%20He%20was%20talking%20about%20Uber's%20plans%20for%20growing%20its%20same-day%20delivery%20network%20with%20merchants%20spanning%20from%20Apple%20to%20Walmart.%20%26quot%3BUltimately%20what%20we%20want%20to%20do%20is%20empower%20every%20single%20local%20merchant%20to%20out-Amazon%20Amazon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhosrowshahi%20traveled%20to%20Switzerland%20after%20attending%20festivities%20in%20DC%20for%20%3Cstrong%3EDonald%20Trump's%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20inauguration%2C%20where%20he%20described%20seeing%20a%20reinvigorated%20sense%20of%20optimism%20among%20business%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BYou%20see%20it%2C%20whether%20you%20agree%20with%20the%20executive%20orders%20or%20not%2C%20there's%20a%20sense%20that%20there's%20a%20window%2C%20there's%20a%20permission%20to%20move%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EHugh%20Langley%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cbfb74d1-e92e-415d-9587-50b3413152f0%5C%22%3EDavos%20is%20already%20prepping%20for%202026%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20conference%20doesn't%20technically%20wrap%20until%20midday%20Friday%2C%20but%20things%20are%20already%20winding%20down.%20Some%20people%20leave%20Thursday%2C%20while%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20the%20delegates%20head%20out%20early%20Friday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20an%20end%20is%20just%20a%20new%20beginning%2C%20and%20that's%20the%20case%20for%20Davos%20%E2%80%A6%202026.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlanning%20for%20next%20year's%20event%20has%20already%20begun.%20Plenty%20of%20companies%20will%20lock%20down%20their%20spaces%20along%20the%20Promenade%20%E2%80%94%20the%20main%20street%20that%20runs%20through%20town%20where%20retail%20shops%20are%20transformed%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bhaus%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20business%20renting%20it%20%