0through%20the%20proposed%20Prevention%20of%20Electronic%20Crimes%20Act.%20The%20law%20seeks%20to%20create%20an%20agency%20to%20control%20social%20media%20content%2C%20impose%20registration%20requirements%2C%20and%20penalize%20disinformation%20with%20imprisonment%2C%20continuing%20the%20crackdown%20ahead%20of%20last%20year's%20contested%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistani-government-proposes-sweeping-controls-on-social-media%2Farticleshow%2F117485419.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistani-government-proposes-sweeping-controls-on-social-media%2Famp_articleshow%2F117485419.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistani-government-proposes-sweeping-controls-on-social-media%2Famp_articleshow%2F117485419.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20launched%204%20startups%20that%20failed%20before%20my%20current%20venture%20took%20off.%20The%20lessons%20I%20learned%20helped%20me%20make%206%20figures%20a%20month.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20man%20sits%20in%20a%20brown%20leather%20chair%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679123df2fcded5e90743b71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBlake%20Nubar%20is%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Laptop%20Freedom.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Blake%20Nubar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBlake%20Nubar%20became%20a%20successful%20entrepreneur%20after%20starting%20and%20navigating%20four%20failed%20startups.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMastering%20digital%20marketing%20and%20pivoting%20from%20agency-style%20work%20to%20products%20was%20his%20turning%20point.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20now%20runs%20a%20digital%20marketing%20company%2C%20invests%20in%20real%20estate%2C%20and%20travels%20extensively.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fblakenubar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBlake%20Nubar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20business%20owner%20in%20Florida.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20the%20financial%20claims.%20This%20story%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20studied%20business%20management%20in%20college%2C%20focusing%20on%20entrepreneurship%2C%20and%20graduated%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20dead%20broke%2C%20so%20I%20started%20on%20a%20traditional%20career%20path.%20I%20dreamed%20of%20entrepreneurship%20but%20didn't%20have%20the%20money%20to%20start%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%2015%20years%20later%2C%20I'm%20now%20a%20successful%20entrepreneur%20making%20six%20figures%20a%20month%20from%20my%20business%2C%20but%20it%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20failures%20to%20get%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257642f51-9ea4-48c2-ba05-ef5105a606c0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20first%20job%20was%20at%20an%20engineering%20firm%2C%20which%20funded%20my%20first%20startup%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20my%20paychecks%20to%20fund%20my%20first%20business%20venture%2C%20Footpriint%2C%20a%20mobile%20app%20that%20allowed%20college%20students%20to%20access%20campus%20events.%20I%20had%20never%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-built-app-no-code-knowledge-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeveloped%20an%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20there%20was%20a%20huge%20learning%20curve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20created%20a%20spec%20document%20outlining%20exactly%20what%20the%20app%20would%20do%20and%20then%20hired%20a%20development%20team%20on%20Elance%20(now%20known%20as%20Upwork).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20my%20inexperience%2C%20I%20didn't%20know%20that%20the%20resources%20needed%20to%20pull%20a%20project%20like%20this%20off%20were%20far%20greater%20than%20I%20could%20supply.%20Funds%20became%20tight%20as%20I%20got%20further%20into%20the%20project%2C%20and%20I%20couldn't%20invest%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227fe22e82-36e8-4bda-871b-b37f870d994e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20my%20first%20startup%20failed%2C%20a%209-5%20job%20was%20still%20not%20how%20I%20pictured%20my%20future%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20told%20what%20to%20do%20at%20my%20job%20and%20when%2C%20and%20essentially%20being%20capped%20at%20what%20I%20could%20earn%2C%20didn't%20align%20with%20how%20I%20saw%20my%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20next%20started%20a%20business%20in%202012%20called%20Learn%20Everywhere%2C%20a%20digital%20product%20business%20that%20failed%20soon%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20my%20engineering%20job%20in%202013%20and%20took%20a%20job%20at%20a%20private%20equity%20company%20that%20funded%20startups.%20This%20new%20job%20gave%20me%20more%20income%20for%20my%20next%20idea%3A%20a%20company%20called%20Orator%20that%20my%20friend%20Ace%20and%20I%20started%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrator%20was%20an%20educational%20company%20that%20transformed%20learning%20material%20for%20students%20into%20a%20visual%20product.%20It%20failed%20two%20years%20into%20its%20existence%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20knowledge%20of%20how%20to%20market%20and%20sell%20and%20the%20amount%20teachers%20were%20willing%20to%20spend%20on%20learning%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c832fc68-7972-4f1c-89c6-2805c2831976%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20invited%20into%20my%20fourth%20startup%20in%202015%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20was%20still%20working%20at%20the%20private%20equity%20company%2C%20one%20of%20the%20investors%20took%20me%20out%20to%20dinner%20one%20night%20and%20asked%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20join%20him%20in%20starting%20a%20fitness%20company%20selling%20supplements%20to%20end%20consumers%20and%20educational%20materials%20to%20personal%20trainers.%20With%20a%20background%20in%20developing%20educational%20material%2C%20this%20seemed%20like%20a%20no-brainer.%20I%20left%20my%20job%20at%20the%20private%20equity%20company%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20first%20big%20project%20was%20to%20create%20a%20personal%20training%20certification.%20I%20needed%20help%2C%20so%20I%20began%20team%20building.%20I%20brought%20Ace%20on%20and%20hired%20a%20sales%20rep%20and%20an%20internet%20marketing%20specialist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20spent%20nine%20months%20building%20the%20product%2C%20a%20full%20course%20that%20included%20a%20book%2C%20mobile%20app%2C%20training%20videos%2C%20resources%2C%20and%20templates.%20When%20we%20were%20finally%20ready%20to%20sell%20it%2C%20we%20couldn't.%20I%20had%20no%20background%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearn-six-figures-digital-marketer-time-travel-snowboard-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20marketing%3C%2Fa%3E%20then%2C%20but%20I%20decided%20to%20learn%20it%20out%20of%20frustration%20of%20not%20making%20sales%20yet%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226977f4f2-d0a0-42e3-8515-07289f632cdb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%202016%2C%20I%20left%20the%20fitness%20partnership%20to%20pursue%20online%20marketing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20enough%20savings%20to%20live%20lean%20for%20a%20year.%20I%20invested%20every%20waking%20minute%20in%20developing%20the%20skills%20needed%20to%20become%20a%20successful%20online%20seller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20to%20help%20business%20owners%20and%20entrepreneurs%20learn%20how%20to%20sell%20more%20of%20their%20products%20and%20services%20online%2C%20which%20I%20needed%20in%20previous%20ventures.%20I%20wanted%20to%20teach%20the%20lessons%20I%20had%20learned%20the%20hard%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAce%20and%20I%20cofounded%20a%20digital%20marketing%20company%20called%20Laptop%20Freedom%20in%202017.%20I%20created%20a%20profile%20on%20Upwork%20to%20generate%20interest%2C%20and%20my%20strategy%20was%20to%20undercut%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20client%20I%20had%20this%20opportunity%20with%20was%20Brian%20Page%2C%20an%20online%20entrepreneur%20just%20starting%20out.%20I%20helped%20Brian%20create%20his%20overall%20marketing%20plan.%20We%20generated%20traffic%20by%20advertising%20on%20joint%20venture%20lists%2C%20sold%20%241%20million%20in%20course%20revenue%20in%2043%20days%2C%20and%20finished%20the%20year%20with%20%247%20million%20in%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e74cc97e-d337-4c7b-98f6-2933f9b0fc7d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWord%20traveled%20fast%20about%20Brian's%20success%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20asked%20if%20we%20could%20replicate%20this%20success%20for%20their%20offers%2C%20so%20we%20took%20on%20more%20clients%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshark-tank-kevin-harrington-small-business-marketing-mistakes-2014-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKevin%20Harrington%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20one%20of%20the%20realtors%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillion-dollar-listing-brokers-share-advice-luxury-buyers-sellers-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMillion%20Dollar%20Listing%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20do%20the%20same%20with%20our%20own%20products%20and%20services.%20I%20pivoted%20the%20digital%20marketing%20company%20from%20agency-style%20work%20to%20educational%20products.%20We%20started%20accounts%20on%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%2C%20as%20well%20as%20an%20email%20list%2C%20which%20all%20have%20around%20250%2C000%20followers%20total%20and%20growing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20first%20digital%20product%20was%20completed%20in%202020.%20We%20created%20a%20launch%20campaign%20to%20bring%20it%20to%20market%20that%20utilized%20affiliates%2C%20joint%20venture%20partners%2C%20Facebook%20ads%2C%20and%20my%20current%20audience%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we%20generated%20%24450%2C000%20in%20revenue%20in%20a%20single%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a691b9ec-8634-4223-b9b5-3d481d284eac%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20I%20first%20started%2C%20it%20was%20chaotic%2C%20but%20now%20the%20business%20has%20infrastructure%2C%20processes%2C%20systems%2C%20and%20a%20road%20map%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20created%20systems%20so%20that%20I%20only%20work%20around%2010%20hours%20a%20week%20max%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20project.%20We%20hired%20an%20operations%20manager%20to%20run%20day-to-day%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20use%20customer%20relationship%20management%20software%20for%20front-end%20marketing%20and%20back-end%20client%20fulfillment%2C%20financial%20management%20software%20to%20pay%20employees%20and%20contractors%2C%20and%20operations%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d15014b-2b5d-45dc-8e09-1166de81289b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20use%20my%20income%20to%20invest%20in%20real%20estate%20and%20travel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tried%20stocks%20but%20couldn't%20stand%20the%20up-and-down%20volatility%2C%20and%20crypto%20wasn't%20for%20me%20either.%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-to-invest-in-real-estate-make-money%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderstand%20real%20estate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20an%20operator%20%E2%80%94%20my%20business%20partner%20and%20I%20are%20the%20bank%2C%20and%20he%20handles%20the%20logistics.%20We%20invest%20in%20distressed%20residential%20properties%2C%20which%20we%20rehab%20and%20sell%2C%20and%20apartment%20complexes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20use%20the%20money%20I%20make%20to%20travel.%20My%20wife%20and%20I%20travel%20six%20months%20a%20year%20and%20then%20take%20a%20breather.%20We've%20been%20all%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20glad%20I%20overcame%20the%20failures%20because%20my%20businesses%20helped%20me%20create%20a%20life%20of%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhad-4-startups-fail-before-1-took-off-heres-what-learned-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737626702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679124fd2fcded5e90743bf5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhad-4-startups-fail-before-1-took-off-heres-what-learned-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Blake%20Nubar%20had%20watched%20four%20of%20his%20startups%20fail%20by%20the%20time%20he%20started%20Laptop%20Freedom%2C%20a%20digital%20marketing%20company%2C%20in%202017.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Emylee%20Williams)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhad-4-startups-fail-before-1-took-off-heres-what-learned-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20AAP%20vs%20BJP%3A%20Who%20Will%20Charm%20Delhi's%20Middle%20Class%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20battle%20to%20woo%20the%20middle%20class%20has%20heated%20up%20in%20poll-bound%20Delhi.%20The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20in%20its%20bid%20to%20win%20over%20this%20section%20of%20voters%2C%20has%20listed%20seven%20demands%20for%20the%20Centre%20to%20consider%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Budget%3A%20increase%20the%20education%20budget%20from%202%25%20to%2010%25%3B%20cap%20private%20schools%20fees%20and%20provide%20subsidies%20and%20scholarships%20for%20higher%20education%3B%20hike%20the%20health%20budget%20to%2010%25%20and%20remove%20health%20insurance%20tax%3B%20raise%20the%20income%20tax%20exemption%20limit%20from%20Rs%207%20lakh%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh%3B%20abolish%20GST%20on%20essential%20items%3B%20frame%20comprehensive%20retirement%20plans%20for%20senior%20citizens%20and%20provide%20them%20with%20free%20treatment%3B%20and%2C%20restore%20the%20discount%20given%20to%20senior%20citizens%20in%20railways%20(a%20popular%20provision%2C%20now%20abandoned).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Middle%20Class%20Manifesto%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20the%20middle%20class%20in%20India%20has%20been%20a%20loyal%20supporter%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20nationally.%20In%20Delhi%2C%20however%2C%20while%20it%20backs%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20in%20state%20elections%2C%20it%20tends%20to%20side%20with%20the%20AAP.%20However%2C%20this%20time%20around%2C%20it%20won't%20be%20surprising%20if%20the%20BJP%20manages%20to%20make%20a%20dent%20in%20the%20AAP's%20middle-class%20vote%20bank%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20scam%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98Sheesh%20Mahal'%20controversy.%20The%20AAP's%20budget%20demands%20should%20be%20seen%20in%20this%20light%E2%80%94as%20pre-emptive%20measures%20to%20win%20over%20the%20middle%20class%2C%20reeling%20under%20high%20inflation%20and%20taxes.%20It's%20a%20win-win%20for%20the%20party%20either%20way%3A%20if%20these%20demands%20are%20eventually%20reflected%20in%20the%20Union%20Budget%2C%20it%20will%20give%20the%20party%20a%20chance%20to%20claim%20credit%2C%20and%20in%20case%20that%20doesn't%20happen%2C%20it%20gets%20a%20stick%20to%20beat%20the%20BJP%20with.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20poll%20promises%20are%20made%20for%20the%20underprivileged%20classes%2C%20and%20some%20for%20a%20few%20industrialists.%20On%20the%20grounds%20of%20caste%20and%20religion%2C%20other%20parties%20have%20created%20a%20vote%20bank.%20And%20they%20need%20donations%20from%20industrialists%2C%20so%20they%20are%20the%20note%20bank.%20Between%20this%20vote%20bank%20and%20note%20bank%2C%20a%20large%20section%20is%20sandwiched.%20This%20is%20India's%20middle%20class%2C%E2%80%9D%20AAP%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20the%20AAP%20has%20already%20implemented%20in%20Delhi%20the%20first%20and%20third%20of%20its%20list%20of%20demands.%20In%202023-24%2C%20the%20spending%20on%20education%20in%20the%20capital%20was%2024.3%25%2C%20as%20against%20an%20average%20of%2014.7%25%20in%20other%20states%3B%20the%20health%20spending%20in%20the%20same%20year%20was%2013.8%25%2C%20significantly%20more%20than%20India's%20state%20average%20of%206.2%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EShifting%20Priorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20middle%20class%20accounts%20for%2045%25%20of%20Delhi's%20population%2C%20higher%20than%20the%20national%20average%20of%2031%25.%20The%20state's%20per%20capita%20income%20is%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20country%20and%20twice%20the%20national%20average.%20The%20middle%20class%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20backers%20of%20the%20AAP%20and%20its%20anti-corruption%20campaign.%20According%20to%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies'%20(CSDS)%20post-poll%20data%2C%20more%20than%20half%20(53%25)%20of%20the%20voters%20from%20this%20section%20backed%20the%20AAP%20in%202020%2C%20while%2039%25%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP.%20In%20contrast%2C%20in%20the%202024%20general%20election%2C%2050%25%20of%20the%20middle%20class%20backed%20the%20BJP%2C%20while%2032%25%20voted%20for%20the%20AAP%20(a%20gain%20of%2011%20percentage%20points%20for%20the%20BJP%20since%20the%202020%20state%20polls%2C%20and%20a%20loss%20of%2021%20percentage%20points%20for%20the%20AAP).%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20AAP%20in%20this%20election%2C%20got%2016%25%20of%20middle-class%20votes.%20This%20means%20that%20almost%20a%20quarter%20of%20middle-class%20voters%20in%20Delhi%20keep%20swinging%20between%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20AAP.%20As%20much%20as%206%25%20of%20the%20AAP's%2015%25%20lead%20over%20the%20BJP%20in%202020%20could%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20middle%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20assembly%20election%20due%20next%20month%2C%20AAP%20hopes%20that%20its%20claims%20of%20providing%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccheapest%E2%80%9D%20electricity%2C%20free%20water%20and%20mohalla%20clinics%20will%20see%20it%20through.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20targeting%20the%20BJP%20for%20doing%20%E2%80%9Clip%20service%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20middle%20class's%20needs.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20attacking%20the%20very%20core%20of%20AAP's%20%E2%80%98clean'%20image%20by%20playing%20up%20the%20two%20scandals%20that%20have%20rocked%20the%20party%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrowing%20Discontent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20easy%20for%20the%20AAP.%20To%20win%20this%20time%2C%20it%20will%20have%20to%20lure%20back%20around%2010-11%25%20of%20middle-class%20voters%20who%20had%20swung%20towards%20the%20BJP%20in%20last%20year's%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Its%20middle-class%20manifesto%20is%20an%20attempt%20not%20just%20to%20attack%20the%20BJP%20but%20also%20to%20position%20itself%20as%20a%20national%20party%20representing%20India's%20middle%20class.%20Already%2C%20a%20large%20section%20of%20the%20population%20has%20been%20clamouring%20for%20lower%20taxes.%20Even%20in%20the%20national%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP's%20share%20of%20middle-class%20support%20shrunk%20by%203%20percentage%20points%20compared%20to%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20while%20the%20Congress's%20rose%20marginally.%20Before%20every%20Budget%2C%20there%20are%20rumblings%20about%20how%20the%20middle%20class%20has%20been%20milked%20by%20successive%20governments.%20A%20high%20inflation%20rate%20of%205.7%25%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%20coupled%20with%20slow%20wage%20growth%20across%20sectors%20has%20added%20to%20the%20discontent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20