and%20private%20data%20that%20Aaron%20calls%20%26quot%3BMoneyball%20for%20venture%20capital.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%20thing%2C%20the%20firm%20says%20it%20is%20much%20more%20effective%20to%20focus%20on%20which%20startups%20are%20not%20likely%20to%20succeed%20versus%20picking%20the%20winners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20algorithms%20are%20not%20really%20selecting%20needles%20from%20a%20haystack%2C%20as%20much%20as%20removing%20all%20the%20hay%2C%26quot%3B%20Aaron%20explained.%20%26quot%3BOur%20AI%20eliminates%20about%2099%25%20of%20all%20early-stage%20companies%20from%20consideration%2C%20because%20our%20data%20predicts%20these%20companies%20have%20a%20higher%20probability%20of%20failure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20surprising%20thing%20about%20TRAC's%20model%20is%20it%20does%20not%20value%20founders%20as%20predictive.%20Instead%2C%20it%20finds%20the%20291%2C000%20investors%20in%20its%20database%20much%20more%20useful%20for%20determining%20a%20startup's%20success%2C%20especially%20a%20tiny%20number%20of%20just%20about%20247%20top%20angel%20investors%20and%20firms%20it%20calls%20%26quot%3BSuperForecasters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20extraordinary%20investors%20make%20a%20profit%20on%20two-thirds%20of%20their%20positions%20and%20one%20in%20five%20of%20their%20investments%20returns%20over%2010X%2C%26quot%3B%20Aaron%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20TRAC%20declined%20to%20share%20the%20full%20list%20of%20SuperForecasters%20it%20did%20share%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F30-of-the-most-successful-early-stage-investors%23aayush-phumbhra-nectar-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20random%20sampling%20of%2030%20of%20them%20with%20BI%20last%20year.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%202%25%20of%20all%20startups%20attract%20a%20SuperForecaster%20so%20that%20eliminates%20over%2098%25%20of%20all%20startups%20from%20TRAC's%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20acc