C%20you%20can%20have%20both%20exposure%20to%20bitcoin's%20upside%20potential%20and%20protection%20from%20downside%20risk%2C%20says%20Jack%20Ablin%2C%20chief%20investment%20officer%20at%20investment%20firm%20Cresset%20Capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20this%2C%20Ablin%20recommends%20his%20clients%20use%20a%20collar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fstock-options%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoption%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-buy-bitcoin-price-start-investing-wall-street-trump-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvesting%20in%20bitcoin%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20collar%20combines%20two%20trades%3A%20buying%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fput-vs-call-option%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eput%20option%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20selling%20a%20call%20option.%20The%20put%20provides%20downside%20protection%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20price%20drop%2C%20while%20the%20call%20allows%20you%20to%20profit%20up%20to%20a%20certain%20ceiling.%20The%20premium%20from%20selling%20the%20call%20option%20can%20offset%20the%20cost%20of%20buying%20the%20put%20option%2C%20making%20the%20collar%20strategy%20low%20or%20no-cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20great%20way%20to%20tiptoe%20into%20Bitcoin%20without%20feeling%20like%20you%20could%20potentially%20get%20your%20head%20handed%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Ablin%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c6b8b97e-a5cd-4889-a30a-13523a7453ad%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20a%20bitcoin%20collar%20work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20step%20to%20a%20collar%20trade%20is%20to%20own%20the%20underlying%20asset%20%E2%80%94%20in%20this%20case%2C%20bitcoin.%20Ablin%20recommends%20doing%20this%20through%20the%20iShares%20Bitcoin%20Trust%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fibit-stock%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIBIT%3C%2Fa%3E).%20A%20bitcoin%20ETF%20is%20an%20accessible%20avenue%20to%20trade%20cryptocurrency%20without%20needing%20to%20use%20a%20crypto-specific%20platform%20or%20store%20the%20asset%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20step%20is%20to%20buy%20an%20out-of-the-money%20(OTM)%20put%20option%2C%20meaning%20the%20strike%20price%20is%20lower%20than%20the%20underlying%20asset's%20current%20market%20price.%20If%20the%20price%20of%20IBIT%20falls%20below%20the%20strike%20price%20of%20the%20put%20option%2C%20you%20can%20exercise%20the%20put%20by%20selling%20your%20shares%20of%20the%20ETF%20at%20the%20strike%20price%2C%20providing%20downside%20protection.%20It's%20essentially%20an%20insurance%20policy%20that%20guarantees%20you%20can%20sell%20your%20shares%20at%20a%20set%20price%2C%20even%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20to%20benefit%20from%20upside%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20to%20a%20degree%20%E2%80%94%20sell%20an%20OTM%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fcall-option%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecall%20option%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20call%20option%20in%20this%20case%20gives%20someone%20else%20the%20right%20to%20buy%20IBIT%20from%20you%20at%20the%20specified%20strike%20price.%20If%20the%20price%20of%20IBIT%20rises%20above%20the%20strike%20price%20of%20the%20option%2C%20then%20you%20are%20obligated%20to%20sell%20it%20for%20the%20strike%20price%20%E2%80%94%20basically%20at%20a%20discount.%20You%20still%20make%20a%20gain%2C%20but%20the%20upside%20is%20capped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20a%20put%20will%20cost%20a%20fee%2C%20but%20writing%20a%20call%20will%20generate%20a%20premium%20that%20can%20reduce%20or%20entirely%20offset%20the%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20let's%20lay%20out%20an%20example.%20Assuming%20the%20cost%20of%20IBIT%20is%20%2460%20per%20share%20for%20illustrative%20purposes%2C%20an%20investor%20could%20carry%20out%20the%20collar%20strategy%20by%20buying%20a%20put%20with%20a%20strike%20price%20of%20%2455%20for%20a%20%242%20fee.%20This%20guarantees%20they%20can%20sell%20the%20shares%20at%20%2455%20if%20they%20were%20to%20fall%20to%2C%20say%2C%20%2440%20within%20the%20set%20expiration%20period.%20They%20could%20also%20then%20sell%20a%20call%20option%20with%20a%20strike%20price%20of%20%2465%20and%20receive%20a%20%242%20premium.%20If%20IBIT%20rises%20to%2C%20say%2C%20%2468%2C%20they%20have%20to%20sell%20the%20shares%20for%20%2465%20a%20piece.%20They%20still%20still%20lock%20in%20the%208.3%25%20jump%20from%20%2460%20to%20%2465%2C%20but%20that's%20the%20maximum%20gain%20they'll%20see.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAblin%20recommends%20investors%20who%20undertake%20this%20strategy%20to%20purchase%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-options-trading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoptions%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20an%20expiration%20period%20of%20one%20year.%20This%20provides%20an%20ample%20time%20horizon%20for%20regulatory%20changes%20or%20other%20catalysts%20to%20play%20out%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a3e7c48-868d-4eda-88be-00544f401bbe%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20cautiously%20bullish%20strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20investors%20who%20are%20comfortable%20with%20limiting%20the%20upper%20bound%20of%20their%20bitcoin%20investment%20in%20exchange%20for%20protection%20from%20a%20large%20drawback%2C%20an%20option%20collar%20provides%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20a%20good%20strategy%20for%20investors%20who%20are%20looking%20to%20add%20bitcoin%20to%20their%20portfolios%20but%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20exposed%20to%20high%20volatility%2C%20Ablin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAblin%20sees%20plenty%20of%20benefit%20from%20a%20bitcoin%20option%20collar.%20The%20cryptocurrency%20could%20have%20a%20bumpy%20future%20ahead%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-cybersecurity-threat-break-encryption-cryptocurrency-bitcoin-blockchain-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equantum%20computing%3C%2Fa%3E%20capabilities%20advance%20and%20threaten%20the%20security%20of%20bitcoin's%20blockchain.%20That's%20not%20to%20mention%20bitcoin's%20history%20of%20multiple%20drawdowns%20in%20excess%20of%2080%25.%20All%20things%20considered%2C%20it%20might%20not%20be%20a%20bad%20idea%20to%20use%20a%20collar%20strategy%20to%20cap%20your%20potential%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-option-strategy-protect-against-crash-trump-crypto-collar-ibit-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737626402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67912b892fcded5e90743ed2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-option-strategy-protect-against-crash-trump-crypto-collar-ibit-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20bitcoin%20option%20collar%20can%20provide%20downside%20protection%20at%20little%20to%20no%20cost.%20Heres%20how%2C%20according%20to%20Cresset%20Capital%20CIO%20Jack%20Ablin.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cji%40businessinsider.com%20(Christine%20Ji)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbitcoin-option-strategy-protect-against-crash-trump-crypto-collar-ibit-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Teen%20who%20killed%203%20girls%20at%20Taylor%20Swift-themed%20dance%20class%20in%20England%20faces%20sentencing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737626149000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117484937%2Cimgsize-1859287.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fteen-who-killed-3-girls-at-taylor-swift-themed-dance-class-in-england-faces-sentencing%