20claimed%20that%20thousands%20of%20vehicle%20with%20Punjab%20registration%20plates%20were%20roaming%20around%20in%20Delhi%2C%20implying%20that%20AAP%20was%20bringing%20people%20from%20Punjab%20--%20where%20it%20is%20in%20power%20--%20to%20Delhi%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20influence%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPunjab%20CM%2C%20all%20the%20ministers%20and%20MLAs%20of%20Punjab%20have%20come%20here%20only%20for%20the%20New%20Delhi%20constituency.%20Thousands%20of%20vehicles%20having%20Punjab%20numbers%20are%20moving%20here%20-%20who%20are%20there%20in%20those%20vehicles%3F%20Republic%20Day%20preparations%20are%20going%20on%2C%20what%20big%20thing%20these%20people%20are%20going%20to%20do%20that%20may%20compromise%20our%20security%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20has%20raised%20the%20issue%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20Delhi%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Verma%20alleged%20that%20Punjab%20government%20employees%20were%20being%20brought%20to%20Delhi%20to%20campaign%20for%20AAP.%20%26quot%3BThese%20individuals%20are%20masquerading%20as%20AAP%20workers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20drew%20fire%20from%20AAP%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20lakhs%20of%20Punjabis%20living%20in%20Delhi%20whose%20families%20and%20ancestors%20have%20made%20countless%20sacrifices%20for%20the%20country.%20Lakhs%20of%20Punjabi%20refugees%20also%20live%20in%20Delhi%20who%20left%20everything%20behind%20during%20the%20difficult%20times%20of%20partition%20and%20settled%20in%20Delhi.%20Their%20families%20have%20also%20suffered%20numerous%20hardships%2C%26quot%3B%20Kejriwal%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20things%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20saying%20today%20are%20insulting%20the%20martyrdom%20and%20sacrifice%20(of%20Punjabis).%20I%20felt%20very%20sad%20to%20hear%20this%20statement.%20Delhi%20is%20ruled%20by%20Punjabis.%20By%20calling%20Punjabis%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20country%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20insulted%20lakhs%20of%20Punjabis%20living%20in%20Delhi.%20BJP%20should%20apologise%20to%20the%20Punjabis%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mann%20said%20there%20is%20no%20restriction%20on%20people%20from%20any%20corner%20of%20the%20country%20visiting%20the%20national%20capital.%20%26quot%3BListen%20to%20this%20statement%20of%20BJP.%20This%20is%20extremely%20dangerous%2C%20worrying%20and%20insulting%20to%20Punjabis.%20They%20are%20marking%20vehicles%20with%20Punjab%20number%20plates%20and%20asking%20why%20are%20vehicles%20from%20Punjab%20roaming%20in%20Delhi.%20They%20are%20saying%20as%20if%20Punjabis%20are%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20security%20of%20the%20country.%20This%20is%20extremely%20insulting%20to%20me%20and%20every%20Punjabi%20in%20the%20country.%20Today%20every%20Punjabi%20is%20feeling%20extremely%20pained%20and%20insulted.%20It%20is%20not%20right%20to%20question%20the%20patriotism%20of%20Punjabis%20in%20this%20way%20for%20your%20dirty%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notices%20to%20Mr%20Verma%20have%20been%20sent%20by%20lawyers%20on%20the%20behalf%20of%20different%20individuals%20based%20out%20of%20Delhi%20as%20well%20as%20Punjab.%20The%20notices%20underline%20how%20the%20BJP%20leader's%20remarks%20have%20hurt%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20Punjabi%20community%20and%20demand%20a%20public%20apology.%20The%20notices%20warn%20of%20further%20legal%20action%20if%20he%20did%20not%20apologise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notices%20also%20stress%20the%20sacrifices%20made%20by%20Punjabis%20for%20the%20country%20and%20add%20that%20Mr%20Verma's%20remarks%20make%20members%20of%20the%20community%20feel%20alienated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20implication%20that%20these%20individuals%20pose%20a%20security%20threat%2C%20especially%20in%20light%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%2C%20is%20both%20baseless%20and%20misleading%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20notices%20says.%20Another%20says%20it%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bclear%20example%20of%20hate%20speech%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20notices%20says%20Mr%20Verma's%20remarks%20%26quot%3Binsult%20a%20community%20that%20has%20contributed%20significantly%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20wrongly%20painting%20them%20as%20potential%20wrongdoers%20in%20light%20of%20national%20security%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20kind%20of%20rhetoric%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20incite%20violence%20and%20promote%20discord%2C%20which%20is%20utterly%20reprehensible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20two-time%20MP%2C%20Mr%20Verma%20is%20contesting%20the%20Delhi%20polls%20from%20the%20New%20Delhi%20seat%20this%20time.%20He%20is%20up%20against%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Congress's%20Sandeep%20Dikshit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AD%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%8F%20%E0%A4%97%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%A1%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%94%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%AC%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%9C%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%A1%E0%A4%BC%E0%A5%8B%E0%A5%A4%20%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%97%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%A1%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%94%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%8F%20%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%BC%E0%A4%AE%20%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%B8%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%9B%20%E0%A4%AD%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%8B%20%3A%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%8D%E