ed%20into%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20No%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusiness.facebook.com%2Fbusiness%2Fhelp%2F1214053053024003%3Flocale%3Den_US%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBreakthrough%20bonus%20programme%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20paid%20the%20money%20during%20their%20first%2090%20days%20on%20the%20app%2C%20so%20long%20as%20they%20post%20regularly.%20They%20will%20get%20the%20cash%20based%20on%20%26quot%3Ban%20evaluation%20of%20your%20social%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20sharing%20content%20across%20Meta's%20platforms%2C%20creators%20will%20also%20get%20access%20to%20Facebook's%20content%20monetization%20program%20that%20enables%20users%20to%20earn%20additional%20income%20from%20their%20posts.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20bonuses%2C%20Meta%20is%20also%20offering%20these%20popular%20faces%20a%20free%20trial%20of%20Meta%20Verified--%20the%20sought-after%20blue%20checkmark%20that%20provides%20exclusive%20features%20and%20helps%20accounts%20stand%20out.%20Normally%2C%20this%20feature%20comes%20at%20a%20monthly%20cost%20ranging%20from%20%2415%20to%20%24120.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeta%20Going%20After%20TikTokers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Meta%20did%20not%20say%20the%20tempting%20cash%20offer%20was%20exclusively%20for%20TikTokers%2C%20it%20came%20just%20days%20after%20the%20rival%20platform%20was%20removed%20from%20US%20app%20stores.%20Though%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20delayed%20the%20short%20video%20app's%20departure%20from%20the%20US%20market%20by%2075%20days%2C%20TikTok%20still%20remains%20unavailable%20to%20download%20from%20app%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20timing%20of%20Meta's%20offer%20suggests%20it%20is%20attempting%20to%20capitalise%20on%20the%20uncertainty%20surrounding%20the%20ByteDance-owned%20platform's%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20TikTok%2C%20it%20has%20170%20million%20users%20in%20the%20US%20-%20many%20of%20whose%20