20during%20a%20burglary%20attempt%20at%20his%20Mumbai%20home%2C%20he%20faces%20a%20legal%20fight%20over%20his%20family's%20property%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20estimated%20to%20be%20worth%20around%20Rs%2015%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20recently%20lifted%20the%20stay%20on%20his%20ancestral%20property%20and%20the%20actor%20may%20lose%20it%20to%20the%20government%20under%20the%20Enemy%20Property%20Act%2C%201968.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Faks6ai1_pataudi-properties_625x300_21_January_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Legal%20Headache%20For%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor's%20family%20owns%20multiple%20properties%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20including%20the%20Flag%20Staff%20House%2C%20where%20he%20spent%20his%20childhood%2C%20Noor-Us-Sabah%20Palace%2C%20Dar-Us-Salam%2C%20Bungalow%20of%20Habibi%2C%20Ahmedabad%20Palace%20and%20Kohefiza%20Property%2C%20among%20others.%20Mr%20Khan%20inherited%20this%20property%20from%20his%20grandmother%20Sajida%20Sultan.%20Sajida%20Sultan%20was%20the%20daughter%20of%20Bhopal's%20last%20Nawab%20Hamidullah%20Khan.%20Hamidullah%20Khan's%20eldest%20daughter%2C%20Abida%20Sultan%2C%20migrated%20to%20Pakistan%20in%201950.%20Her%20sister%2C%20Sajida%2C%20stayed%20on%20in%20India%20and%20married%20Iftikhar%20Ali%20Khan%20Pataudi%2C%20the%20Nawab%20of%20Pataudi%20and%20Mr%20Khan's%20grandfather.%20Sajida%20inherited%20her%20father's%20property%20and%20this%20passed%20on%20to%20Mr%20Khan.%20In%202015%2C%20however%2C%20it%20was%20declared%20that%20Abida%20was%20the%20legal%20heir%20to%20her%20father's%20assets%20and%20since%20she%20migrated%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20they%20can%20be%20acquired%20by%20the%20government%20under%20the%20Enemy%20Property%20Act.%20A%202019%20order%20recognised%20Sajida%20as%20the%20heir%20and%20brought%20relief%20to%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20latest%20order%20is%20a%20fresh%20headache%20for%20the%20family%20and%20Mr%20Khan%20and%20his%20mother%20and%20veteran%20actor%20Sharmila%20Tagore%20must%20navigate%20this%20to%20reclaim%20their%20family%20property.%20For%20clarity%2C%20the%20Enemy%20Property%20Act%20allows%20the%20Centre%20to%20claim%20properties%20owned%20by%20individuals%20who%20migrated%20to%20Pakistan%20post-Partition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fd13nYQsgqPY%3Fsi%3DekCeyldDJdcgGfjw%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'A%20Nawab%20With%20No%20Inheritance'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%202019%20interview%20with%20Midday%2C%20Mr%20Khan%20had%20said%20that%20he%20had%20buy%20back%20the%20Pataudi%20Palace%20in%20Gurugram%20after%20the%20death%20of%20his%20father%20and%20ace%20cricketer%20Mansoor%20Ali%20Khan%20Pataudi.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20my%20father%20died%2C%20it%20was%20rented%20to%20the%20Neemrana%20Group%20of%20Hotels.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20that%20the%20hotel%20group%20told%20him%20that%20if%20he%20wanted%20it%20back%2C%20he%20would%20have%20to%20pay%20%26quot%3Blots%20of%20money%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20then%20earned%20and...%20so%20even%20the%20house%20that's%20supposedly%20inherited%20has%20been%20earned%20back%20through%20money%20from%20films%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20nothing%2C%20there%20is%20some%20history%20and%20culture%2C%20beautiful%20photographs%20and%20of%20course%2C%20some%20land%20and%20it%20has%20been%20a%20privileged%20upbringing%2C%20but%20there%20has%20been%20no%20inheritance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20actor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20has%20said%20he%20was%20born%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20but%20subsequently%20lived%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20Pataudi%20(Gurugram)%20and%20Delhi.%C2%A0Mr%20Khan%20said%20during%20the%20interview%20that%20it%20was%20his%20grandmother%2C%20Sajida%2C%20who%20was%20looking%20after%20the%20family's%20properties%20in%20Bhopal.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20she%20got%20old%2C%20we%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20to%20live%20with%20her.%20Nice%2C%20big%20old%20house%20in%20Delhi%20which%20she%20had%20been%20given%20for%20her%20lifetime.%20in%20return%20for%20land%20and%20property%20and%20all%20those%20kind%20of%20deals%20that%20these%20old%20families%20had%20made%20with%20the%20Indian%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FMvaBm3d6Mkc%3Fsi%3Dcirk571nCP56wnNy%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaif's%20Chat%20With%20NDTV%20When%20He%20Became%20Nawab%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20caught%20up%20with%20Mr%20Khan%20in%20October%202011%2C%20shortly%20after%20his%20father%20died%20and%20he%20became%20the%20titular%20Nawab%20of%20Pataudi.%20Speaking%20to%20veteran%20journalist%20Shekhar%20Gupta%20in%20the%20popular%20show%20Walk%20The%20Talk%2C%20Mr%20Khan%20spoke%20about%20his%20father's%20death%20due%20to%20an%20acute%20lung%20infection.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20possibly%20one%20of%20the%20most%20disturbing%20and%20painful%20ways%20to%20go.%20It%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20mind%20of%20its%20own%2C%20this%20disease.%20It%20can%20either%20stall%20or%20accelerate%2C%20we%20don't%20know%20anything%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20same%20interview%2C%20Mr%20Khan%20had%20explained%20how%20his%20family%20approached%20their%20nawab%20status.%20%26quot%3BMy%20grandfather%20was%20more%20famous%20for%20getting%20a%20hundred%20against%20the%20Australians%20and%20then%20saying%20he%20doesn't%20want%20to%20play%20bodyline.%20So%20gentlemanly%20act%20of%20genuine%20chivalry.%26quot%3B%20Iftikhar%20Ali%20Khan%20Pataudi%20is%20the%20only%20Test%20cricketer%20to%20have%20played%20for%20both%20India%20and%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20father%20was%2C%20again%2C%20less%20as%20a%20nawab%2C%20of%20course%20there%20is%20his%20lungi%20and%20kurta%20and%20his%20liking%20for%20classical%20music%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20with%20parents%20Tiger%20Pataudi%20and%20Sharmila%20Tagore%20and%20sisters%20Soha%20and%20Saba%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20with%20parents%20Tiger%20Pataudi%20and%20Sharmila%20Tagore%20and%20sisters%20Soha%20and%20Saba%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F1g152f_pataudi-family_625x300_23_January_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaif%20Ali%20Khan%20with%20parents%20Tiger%20Pataudi%20and%20Sharmila%20Tagore%20and%20sisters%20Soha%20and%20Saba%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaif%20Ali%20Khan's%20'Nawabzade'%20anecdote%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20interview%2C%20Mr%20Khan%20had%20said%20films%20show%20nawabs%20with%20a%20negative%20connotation%20and%20narrated%20an%20awkward%20incident%20during%20the%20shooting%20of%20the%202000%20film%20Kya%20Kehna.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20dialogue%20in%20which%20one%20of%20the%20chaps%20catches%20me%20because%20I%20am%20not%20being%20very%20nice%20to%20his%20sister%20and%20says%2C%20haraamzada%20(meaning%20bastard).%20There%20were%20some%20sensor%20problems%20and%20we%20had%20to%20dub%20over%20haraamzada.%20The%20producer%2C%20director%20said%20'just%20say%20nawabzaada%2C%20it's%20the%20same%20thing'.%20I%20said%2C%20'really%3F