C%20Joe%20Velaidum%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Laura%20Kelly%2C%20got%20home%20after%20walking%20their%20dogs.%20They%20noticed%20their%20brick%20sidewalk%20was%20covered%20with%20dusty%20debris%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20a%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rare%20recording%20on%20their%20doorbell%20camera%20showed%20a%20fast-moving%20space%20rock%20crashing%20into%20the%20ground%2C%20causing%20a%20massive%20explosion%20of%20grey%20dust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMeteorite%20impact%20recorded%20by%20a%20doorbell%20camera%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FFL0VpH2yQL%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FFL0VpH2yQL%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20curious%20side%20of%20%F0%9D%95%8F%20(%40curioXities)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FcurioXities%2Fstatus%2F1879817079748251850%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2016%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20stop%20on%20that%20spot%20-%20ever%20and%20looking%20back%20on%20it%20now%2C%20we%20noticed%2C%20because%20of%20the%20video%2C%20if%20I%20had%20stayed%20on%20that%20very%20spot%20for%20just%20two%20minutes%20longer%2C%20I%20absolutely%20would%20have%20been%20struck%20and%20probably%20killed%20by%20this%20meteor%2C%26quot%3B%20Joe%20Velaidum%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2025%2F01%2F22%2Fscience%2Fmeteorite-strike-doorbell-camera%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20later%2C%20a%20lab%20analysis%20confirmed%20it%20was%20indeed%20a%20rock%20that%20fell%20from%20space.%20The%20object%20was%20then%20formally%20included%20in%20a%20database%20maintained%20by%20the%20non-profit%20Meteoritical%20Society.%20The%20specimen%20was%20named%20%26quot%3BCharlottetown%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20city%20on%20Prince%20Edward%20Island%20in%20eastern%20Canada%20where%20it%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%2069%20meteorites%20have%20been%20discovered%20and%20registered%20nationwide%2C%20the%20Charlottetown%20meteorite%20stands%20out%20due%20to%20its%20accompanying%20video.%20Although%20the%20doorbell%20clip%20showing%20its%20arrival%20is%20not%20the%20first%20to%20be%20captured%20on%20camera%2C%20it%20is%20noteworthy%20as%20the%20incident%20was%20recorded%20at%20very%20close%20range%20and%20with%20sound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20the%20best%20of%20my%20knowledge%2C%20it's%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20meteorite%20hitting%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20Earth%20has%20been%20recorded%20on%20video%20with%20sound%2C%26quot%3B%20said%C2%A0Chris%20Herd%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20Earth%20and%20Atmospheric%20Sciences%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Alberta%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20space%20rocks%20that%20strike%20Earth's%20atmosphere%20go%20unnoticed%20because%20they%20either%20burn%20up%20before%20they%20can%20reach%20the%20surface%20or%20land%20in%20remote%20places.%20A%20few%20people%20have%20ever%20been%20near%20a%20meteorite%20at%20the%20precise%20moment%20of%20impact%2C%20and%20the%20likelihood%20of%20seeing%20one%20happen%20firsthand%20is%20exceedingly%20unlikely.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737607980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fu288jp98_canada-meteorite-strike-outside-home_625x300_23_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdoorbell-camera-records-a-meteorite-striking-front-walkway-in-canada-7538387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rare%20recording%20showed%20a%20fast-moving%20space%20rock%20unexpectedly%20crashing%20into%20the%20ground%20with%20a%20loud%20bang%20and%20a%20massive%20explosion%20of%20grey%20dust.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22htt